
- IF WE ARE NOT USING LOMBOK THEN WE HAVE TO MANUALLY ADD THE JAR OF APACHE LOG4J TO OUR POM.XML FILE
- LOGGER IS A INTERFACE AND HENCE WE CANNOT CREATE AN OBJECT OF IT, SO WE HAVE TO

#For logging- check this in application.properties

%d-date
%m-message
%n- new line
%p- logging level
%c- class name
%M- method name
%t- thread

